content:
N.Y. Comp. Codes R. & Regs. Tit. 17 ยง 8106.27 - Town of Ellicott

State Regulations
(a) Strunk

Road. The northbound and southbound roadways of Strunk Road between exit 11 of

Route 17, the Southern Tier Expressway, and Route 430. (b) The eastbound and westbound roadways of

Route 394 between exit 13 of Route 17, the Southern Tier Expressway, and Water

Street. (c) The northbound and
southbound roadways of Water Street between Route 394 and Elmwood

Avenue. (d) The eastbound and
westbound roadways of Elmwood Avenue between Water Street and Harmon

Avenue. (e) The northbound and
southbound roadways of Harmon Avenue between Elmwood Avenue and the terminus of

Harmon Avenue. (f) Allen Street. Allen Street between South Work Street and the Sysco Food Services Incorporated
terminal. (g) Allen Street. Allen

Street between CR 71 (South Work Street) to CR 105 (Buffalo Street) in the

Village of Falconer and the Town of Ellicott. Notes
